    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age both inside and out. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up to address some minor rattling. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming weekend projects.",
