    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there! It truly breaks my heart to let this absolute gem go, but it's time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered. I\u2019ve spent more weekends than I can count polishing this beauty, and honestly, she still has that 'fresh off the lot' magic. It\u2019s been my pride and joy\u2014garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and driven with a lot of love. If you're looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, you've found it. I'd love for a fellow enthusiast to take the wheel and enjoy every mile. Come by for a coffee and a look\u2014you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
