      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted specimen of automotive engineering. This isn't your average commuter; it's a turn-key platform with a razor-sharp throttle response and a linear torque curve that pulls hard all the way to redline. The suspension geometry has been dialed in for optimal turn-in, featuring upgraded bushings to eliminate any deflection under high-G loads. Externally, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating that yields a mirror-like finish. The engine bay is clinically clean, showing zero signs of thermal cycling fatigue on the gaskets or fluid seepage. Gear shifts are crisp with positive engagement, indicating a perfectly healthy synchro set. This is a rare opportunity to own a machine that has been maintained to an exacting standard.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
